%% State Transition Diagram: Complete FYP System Lifecycle
%% Shows all possible states and transitions across all iterations

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle : System Ready
    
    Idle --> ValidatingPrompt : User submits prompt
    Idle --> VoiceInput : Voice input mode
    Idle --> ChatMode : Interactive chat mode
    
    %% Voice Input Branch
    VoiceInput --> ProcessingSpeech : Voice detected
    ProcessingSpeech --> TranscribingAudio : STT processing
    TranscribingAudio --> ValidatingPrompt : Text transcribed
    TranscribingAudio --> ErrorSTTFailure : Transcription failed
    
    %% Chat Mode Branch  
    ChatMode --> ProcessingChat : Chat message received
    ProcessingChat --> GeneratingResponse : Chatbot processing
    GeneratingResponse --> ChatMode : Response generated
    GeneratingResponse --> ErrorChatFailure : Chat generation failed
    
    %% Main Story Generation Flow
    ValidatingPrompt --> EnhancingPrompt : Prompt is valid
    ValidatingPrompt --> ErrorInvalidPrompt : Prompt is invalid/nonsense
    
    EnhancingPrompt --> DetectingLanguage : Prompt enhanced
    DetectingLanguage --> DeterminingAgeGroup : Language detected
    DeterminingAgeGroup --> GeneratingStory : Age group determined
    
    GeneratingStory --> ReviewingContent : Story generated (3 scenes)
    GeneratingStory --> RetryGeneration : JSON parse error
    GeneratingStory --> ErrorGenerationFailure : Max retries exceeded
    
    RetryGeneration --> GeneratingStory : Retry attempt (max 2)
    
    ReviewingContent --> EditingFormatting : Quality validated
    ReviewingContent --> ErrorContentRejection : Content rejected
    
    EditingFormatting --> GeneratingPDF : Content polished
    EditingFormatting --> ApplyingStyleGuide : Style formatting
    
    ApplyingStyleGuide --> GeneratingPDF : Style applied
    
    GeneratingPDF --> CheckImageToggle : PDF created
    
    CheckImageToggle --> GeneratingImages : Images enabled
    CheckImageToggle --> CheckAudioToggle : Images disabled
    
    CheckAudioToggle --> GeneratingAudio : Audio enabled
    CheckAudioToggle --> SavingStory : Audio disabled
    
    %% Image Generation States
    GeneratingImages --> ProcessingCharacterConsistency : Images generated
    ProcessingCharacterConsistency --> ApplyingStyleTransfer : Consistency applied
    ApplyingStyleTransfer --> UpscalingImages : Style transfer complete
    UpscalingImages --> SavingImages : Upscaling complete
    SavingImages --> CheckAudioToggle : Images saved
    
    GeneratingImages --> SavingStory : Image generation failed<br/>(graceful degradation)
    
    %% Audio Generation States
    GeneratingAudio --> SynthesizingSpeech : Audio generation started
    SynthesizingSpeech --> ApplyingVoiceEffects : Speech synthesized
    ApplyingVoiceEffects --> SavingAudio : Voice effects applied
    SavingAudio --> SavingStory : Audio saved
    
    GeneratingAudio --> SavingStory : Audio generation failed<br/>(graceful degradation)
    
    %% Story Saving and Evaluation
    SavingStory --> SpawningEvaluation : Story saved to file
    SavingStory --> UpdatingUserPreferences : Learning from interaction
    
    UpdatingUserPreferences --> SpawningEvaluation : Preferences updated
    
    SpawningEvaluation --> Completed : Evaluation started in background
    
    Completed --> [*] : Return to frontend
    Completed --> InteractiveMode : Interactive features enabled
    
    %% Interactive Mode States
    InteractiveMode --> WaitingForInput : Ready for user interaction
    WaitingForInput --> ProcessingUserInput : User provides input
    ProcessingUserInput --> GeneratingResponse : Input processed
    GeneratingResponse --> InteractiveMode : Response ready
    WaitingForInput --> [*] : User exits
    
    %% Error States
    ErrorInvalidPrompt --> [*] : Return error to user
    ErrorGenerationFailure --> [*] : Return error to user
    ErrorContentRejection --> [*] : Return error to user
    ErrorSTTFailure --> [*] : Return error to user
    ErrorChatFailure --> [*] : Return error to user
    
    note right of ValidatingPrompt
        Prompt Agent classifies:
        - normal
        - detailed  
        - invalid
        - nonsense
        + language detection
        + age group determination
    end note
    
    note right of GeneratingStory
        Writer Agent uses Ollama
        with retry logic (up to 2 attempts)
        for JSON parsing failures
        + character development
        + dialogue generation
    end note
    
    note right of GeneratingImages
        Advanced generation:
        1. txt2img with character consistency
        2. img2img hires fix
        3. style transfer
        4. upscaling
        Takes 60-120s per scene on GPU
    end note
    
    note right of GeneratingAudio
        TTS processing:
        1. Text-to-speech synthesis
        2. Voice effect application
        3. Emotion detection
        4. Audio optimization
    end note
    
    note right of SpawningEvaluation
        Non-blocking subprocess
        Evaluation runs in background
        Does not delay response
        + user preference learning
    end note
    
    note right of InteractiveMode
        Real-time features:
        - Voice interaction
        - Chat responses
        - Dynamic story modification
        - User preference adaptation
    end note

